Milestones

Milestones represent required, time-dependent steps in your support process. They ensure agents resolve support records correctly and on time.

Available in: Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions with the Service Cloud

An entitlement process can have up to 10 milestones. You can set up a milestone to occur once or recur until the entitlement process exits.

Before using milestones, review Milestone Limitations.

Set Up Milestones
Milestones represent required steps in your support management process, like first response times. Set them up and customize in your org so they can be added to entitlement processes and applied to support records.

Work with Milestones
Milestones help give customers a consistent support experience. Learn about milestones statues, actions, and recurrence types.
